{"title":"localtion对象常用的属性、方法","slug":"localtion对象常用的属性、方法","date":"2017-09-20T01:59:08.784Z","updated":"2017-09-11T14:31:35.033Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"localtion对象常用的属性、方法\"><a href=\"#localtion对象常用的属性、方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"localtion对象常用的属性、方法\"></a>localtion对象常用的属性、方法</h2></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>页面跳转</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">location.href = <span class=\"string\">\"页面地址\"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>页面刷新</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">location.reload();</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>获取get请求的参数</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">loaction.search</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>获取锚点/锚名</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">location.hash</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>获取协议的名称</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">location.protocol</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>获取路径名称</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">location.pathname</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":[{"name":"网站搭建","path":"api/categories/网站搭建.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"开发技巧","path":"api/tags/开发技巧.json"}]}